## ⚙️ DevOps & Deployment Infrastructure

The platform runs on a lean, automated architecture synced directly to our production environments.

### 📂 Directory Architecture
```text
├── .github/                   # Automated deployment webhooks
├── assets/                    # Optimized frontend dependencies
│   ├── css/                   # Responsive layout styling
│   ├── js/                    # Core payment & booking logic
│   └── images/                # Highly compressed wildlife & lodge media assets
├── templates/                 # Reusable structural components (Nav, Footer)
├── .gitignore                 # Exclusion rules for local environment credentials
├── index.html                 # Main landing portal
└── README.md                  # System documentation (This file)
```

### 🌐 Target Production Path
Code merged into the production branch triggers automated synchronization with the host control panel filesystem:
```path
domains/rutssafaris.co.ke/public_html/
```

